    "taxonomy": "Bulbophyllum rotundatum is classified within the plant kingdom as belonging to the family Orchidaceae, which is commonly known as the orchid family. This classification places it within the order Asparagales. At the genus level, it is classified as a member of the Bulbophyllum genus, which is a large and diverse group of orchids. Within the Bulbophyllum genus, Bulbophyllum rotundatum is further classified based on its unique characteristics and features. The specific classification of Bulbophyllum rotundatum within the Bulbophyllum genus may require additional information or research.",
